<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box;">
  <h1 style="color: #4CAF50; font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 20px;">Dear Dr. <%= @appointment.doctor.full_name %>,</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #333;">
    We regret to inform you that your appointment with <%= @appointment.patient.full_name %> scheduled for <%= @appointment.scheduled_time.strftime("%d/%m/%Y at %I:%M %p") %> has been cancelled.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #333;">
    We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. Our team will contact the patient shortly to reschedule the appointment.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #333;">
    For more details about the appointment, click the following link:<br>
    <%= link_to "#{@appointment.title}", appointment_url(@appointment, host: 'localhost:3000') %>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #333;">
    If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #333;">
    Thank you for your understanding,<br>
    WellCare Team
  </p>
</div>
